5. MODEL TRAINING INFRASTRUCTURE

5.1 Hardware Specifications

```
TRAINING HARDWARE CLUSTER:

PRIMARY TRAINING NODES (1000 nodes):
├── CPU: AMD EPYC 9654 (96 cores each)
├── GPU: 8× NVIDIA H100 (80GB HBM3) per node
├── Memory: 2TB DDR5 per node
├── Storage: 100TB NVMe per node
├── Network: 400 Gbps InfiniBand
└── Power: 10kW per node

QUANTUM CO-PROCESSORS (16 systems):
├── IBM Quantum System Two: 4 systems
│   └── 1000+ qubits each
├── Google Quantum AI: 4 systems
│   └── 1000+ qubits each
├── D-Wave Advantage2: 4 systems
│   └── 7000+ qubits each
└── Custom Quantum Accelerators: 4 systems
    └── 5000+ qubits each

NEUROMORPHIC PROCESSORS:
├── Intel Loihi 2: 10,000 chips
│   └── 1M neurons per chip
├── IBM TrueNorth: 5,000 chips
│   └── 1M neurons per chip
└── Custom Neuromorphic ASICs: 1,000 chips
    └── 10M neurons per chip

NETWORK INFRASTRUCTURE:
├── Intra-cluster: 400 Gbps InfiniBand
├── Inter-cluster: 100 Gbps dedicated fiber
├── Quantum Network: QKD for secure communication
└── Internet: 10 Gbps connections to research networks

POWER & COOLING:
├── Total Power: 50 MW
├── Power Source: 100% renewable
├── Cooling: Liquid immersion cooling
├── PUE: 1.05 (high efficiency)
└── Backup: 24-hour battery + generators
```

5.2 Training Pipeline Architecture

```
TRAINING WORKFLOW:

PHASE 1: PRE-TRAINING (6 MONTHS)
├── Step 1: Data Preparation (1 month)
│   ├── Dataset: 10 Exabytes
│   ├── Tokenization: 10M vocabulary
│   ├── Sharding: 100,000 shards
│   └── Validation: Quality checks
├── Step 2: Initial Training (3 months)
│   ├── Model: 10T parameters
│   ├── Batch Size: 4M tokens
│   ├── Sequence Length: 1M tokens
│   ├── Optimizer: Quantum AdamW
│   └── Checkpoints: Every 1000 steps
├── Step 3: Convergence Optimization (2 months)
│   ├── Learning Rate Scheduling
│   ├── Gradient Clipping
│   ├── Mixed Precision Training
│   ├── Model Parallelism
│   └── Performance Optimization
└── Output: Base CP-LLM Model

PHASE 2: FINE-TUNING (3 MONTHS)
├── Step 1: Instruction Tuning (1 month)
│   ├── Dataset: 100M expert examples
│   ├── Tasks: 1000+ medical reasoning tasks
│   ├── Methods: Supervised fine-tuning
│   └── Evaluation: Medical exam benchmarks
├── Step 2: Reinforcement Learning (1 month)
│   ├── Reward Models: 10 specialized models
│   ├── Methods: PPO, DPO
│   ├── Human Feedback: 1M preference pairs
│   └── Alignment: Safety & helpfulness
├── Step 3: Specialization (1 month)
│   ├── Clinical Diagnosis: 50M cases
│   ├── Genomic Analysis: 10M sequences
│   ├── Epidemiological Modeling: 100 years data
│   ├── Pharmaceutical: 1M compounds
│   └── Public Health: 100K policy scenarios
└── Output: Specialized CP-LLM Models

PHASE 3: VALIDATION & SAFETY (3 MONTHS)
├── Step 1: Medical Validation (1 month)
│   ├── Diagnostic Accuracy: 100K cases
│   ├── Treatment Recommendations: 50K cases
