│  • Remediation: Automated incident response        │
│  • Escalation: Human-in-the-loop escalation        │
│  • Learning: Continuous improvement feedback       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

KEY MONITORING METRICS:

1. SYSTEM PERFORMANCE METRICS
   ├── Infrastructure
